💻 Installing Python
🔹 Step 1: Download Python

-Official website (always use this):

👉 https://www.python.org/downloads/

Choose:

-Python 3.x (latest version)

-Click Download Python

---

🔹 Step 2: Install Python (IMPORTANT)

-During installation:
✅ Check Add Python to PATH
✅ Click Install Now

⚠️ If you skip “Add Python to PATH”, Python will not work correctly in the terminal.

---
🔹 Step 3: Verify Installation

-Open Command Prompt or PowerShell and type:

python --version


or

py --version

---
If you see a version number → ✅ Python is installed correctly.
